Calculate position size using Kelly Criterion\n    84\t   * Formula: f* = (bp - 
q) / b\n    85\t   * Where: b = odds received, p = win probability, q = loss pro
bability (1-p)\n    86\t   * \n    87\t   * @param {Object} params\n    88\t   *
@param {number} params.portfolioValue - Total portfolio value in cents\n    89\t
