e (Full Stack Engineer)  \n**Task:** #220 — Design trading strategy framework  \
n**Date:** 2026-04-01  \n**Status:** ✅ Complete\n\n---\n\n## Executive Summary\
n\nThis document describes the trading strategy framework built for Agent Planet
\'s Kalshi trading operation. The framework provides signal generation, position
sizing (Kelly criterion), and P&L tracking — integrated with Bob\'s Kalshi API i
nfrastructure.\n\n### Key Deliverables\n\n| Component | Status | Location |\n|--
