ashboard.\n\nLet me prioritize:\n1. Fix the MockPool bug so the PnL endpoints wo
rk\n2. Add aggregate `/api/strategies/pnl` endpoint to Bob\'s server.js\n3. Upda
te status.md\n4. Send messages to Bob and Charlie about the fixes\n\nLet me star
t by fixing the MockPool.',
